OL,3,C2024 'almost certain' to be hottest
OL,4,Cyear on record
OL,6,FExtreme weather is becoming more
OL,7,Fcommon as our climate continues to
OL,8,Fchange and warm, as ITV News' Fred
OL,9,FDimbleby reports
OL,11,FThis year is "virtually certain" to be
OL,12,Fthe world's hottest on record, with
OL,13,Ftemperatures more than 1.5C above pre-
OL,14,Findustrial times for the first time.
OL,16,FGlobal temperatures from January to
OL,17,FOctober were 0.71C higher than the
OL,18,Faverage from 1991-2020, the highest
OL,19,Frecord for the period, data from the
OL,20,FEU's Copernicus Climate Change Service
OL,21,F(C3S) shows.
