OL,3,C2024 'almost certain' to be hottest
OL,4,Cyear on record
OL,6,FThis is 0.16C higher than the same
OL,7,Fperiod for 2023 - the world's hottest
OL,8,Fyear to date.
OL,10,FAs a result, scientists have said it
OL,11,Fis now virtually certain that 2024
OL,12,Fwill be the warmest year on record.
OL,14,FAnd as 2023 was 1.48C above pre-
OL,15,Findustrial levels, according to the
OL,16,FEuropean dataset, it is also virtually
OL,17,Fcertain 2024 will be more than 1.5C
OL,18,Fhigher than before the industrial
OL,19,Frevolution, and likely more than 1.55C
OL,20,Fhigher.
