OL,11,FSamantha Burgess, deputy director of
OL,12,Fthe Copernicus Climate Change Service
OL,13,F(C3S) said: "After 10 months of 2024
OL,14,Fit is now virtually certain that 2024
OL,15,Fwill be the warmest year on record and
OL,16,Fthe first year of more than 1.5C above
OL,17,Fpre-industrial levels according to the
OL,18,FERA5 dataset.
