OL,6,F"This marks a new milestone in global
OL,7,Ftemperature records and should serve
OL,8,Fas a catalyst to raise ambition for
OL,9,Fthe upcoming climate change
OL,10,Fconference, Cop29."
OL,12,FAs Cop29 begins next week, the World
OL,13,FMeteorological Organisation (WMO) is
OL,14,Fdue to publish an overarching analysis
OL,15,Fof global temperatures in 2024,
OL,16,Fdrawing on a series of datasets
OL,17,Fincluding the ERA5 data.
