OL,6,FResponding to the figures, Mike
OL,7,FChilds, head of science, policy and
OL,8,Fresearch at Friends of the Earth,
OL,9,Fsaid: "The time for dither and delay
OL,10,Fis long gone. We need global leaders
OL,11,Fto smash the emergency glass now and
OL,12,Fdo everything in their power to
OL,13,Fprevent further harm."
